commits.message: Update the import path of OpenTelemetry

Merge pull request #914 from ChenX1993/version-2-fix-import

Update the import path of OpenTelemetry

pull_request.title: Update the import path of OpenTelemetry
pull_request.body:
Explicitly adding package - `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/trace` to glide.lock make the import path in code be `go.opentelemetry.io/otel/trace/trace`, which is conflict with the import path internally used (`go.opentelemetry.io/otel/trace`) in the company.

Adding `go.opentelemetry.io/otel` should be enough.

release.body:
## What's Changed
* Use reference type log fields container for context logging by @amolmejari2 in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/891
* Use context logger in panic handler by @amolmejari2 in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/893
* Log fields cleanup by @amolmejari2 in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/882
* Log utils for error tagging by @amolmejari2 in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/895
* Structured error logs in client modules of type tchannel by @amolmejari2 in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/894
* Zanzibar major version upgrade by @chirayu in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/899
* Structured error logs in client modules of type http by @amolmejari2 in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/896
* Support custom import path by @chirayu in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/901
* zap imported in the http client template by @chirayu in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/903
* Expose tracer& tracer closer options in gateway by @ChenX1993 in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/909
* Update tracer option as a tracer provider func by @ChenX1993 in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/910
* add custom default tags to root scope from config by @sonakshi2000 in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/911

## New Contributors
* @amolmejari2 made their first contribution in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/891
* @sonakshi2000 made their first contribution in https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/pull/911

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/uber/zanzibar/compare/v1.2.5...v2.0.1
